You all asked about this bra last time I posted it, so here it is again!! I have been using @misseskissesxo for two years now, and I simply adore this contraption! On a typical day I wear no bra or cloth & elastic bras, but when I’m wearing low cut dresses or just want extra attention on my boobs (lol) this bra is boob heaven. I’m a 30C, and they don’t really smoosh up against each other on their own, so it’s fun to have this as an option for more cleavage!! For example, when I was Elvira for Halloween, I knew I needed to also emulate her boobs for the costume, and this gave me the Elvira tits my heart desired 😂 that was the longest I’d worn a Misses Kisses bra for, and they stayed on until I went home in the wee hours of the morning! Which is rare for me!! Misses Kisses comes in three colors, three different neckline depths, and fits sizes 30A to 50J, and getting it fitted virtually is super easy if you’re not sure how to adjust it. And the code Thongria15 gets ya 15% off 🥰 #ad

Being a co-presenter at the Society of Risk Analysis symposium on sex toy chemicals and microplastics was a fulfilling way to end 2023 💙 very thankful for the scientists and researchers who created the original study which led to this collaboration.
